    "description": "KPIT Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Ranchi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout KPIT Technologies:\nKPIT Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in AWS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with KPIT Technologies!",
